OL,3,CFears growing for future of maternity
OL,4,Cservices at Daisy Hill Hospital
OL,6,FEmergency plans are being drawn up by
OL,7,Fthe Southern Health Trust to try and
OL,8,Fprotect maternity services at Daisy
OL,9,FHill Hospital in Newry.
OL,11,FStaff have voiced concerns that some
OL,12,Fmaternity services at the hospital may
OL,13,Fhave to be temporarily suspended
OL,14,Fbefore a solution can be found.
OL,16,FThe Southern Health Trust has refuted
OL,17,Fthat it plans to pull the service, but
OL,18,Fadmitted that discussions are ongoing
OL,19,Fas to how best stabilise maternity
OL,20,Fservices.
