OL,3,CFears growing for future of maternity
OL,4,Cservices at Daisy Hill Hospital
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson for the
OL,7,FSouthern Health and Social Care Trust
OL,8,Fsaid: "The Southern Trust provides an
OL,9,Farea wide maternity and gynaecology
OL,10,Fservice, across the community and from
OL,11,Four two hospital sites - Daisy Hill
OL,12,FHospital and Craigavon Area Hospital.
OL,14,F"Like many other specialties
OL,15,Fthroughout health and social care,
OL,16,Fobstetrics and gynaecology services
OL,17,Fhave been facing growing staffing
OL,18,Fchallenges, impacting midwifery and
OL,19,Fconsultant teams.
