OL,6,F"We greatly appreciate the flexibility
OL,7,Fof the whole obstetric and gynaecology
OL,8,Fteam and dedication to women, mothers
OL,9,Fand babies in difficult circumstances.
OL,11,F"Work is ongoing to assess how best we
OL,12,Fcan stabilise and safely sustain
OL,13,Fmaternity and gynaecology services
OL,14,Facross the Trust area.
OL,16,F"We appreciate the ongoing support of
OL,17,Ffamilies and the public as we work
OL,18,Fthrough these challenges."
